Before using, the unit needs to be Activated. 
1. Log in your account;
2. Ensure the DBScar connector is in 16 PIN DLC under the dash (see the picture below);
3. Connect the DBScar connector via Bluetooth;
4. Turn the ignition switch to ON position;
Caution: Disconnect the DBScar connector from DLC during the activation will permanent damage the vehicle and device!

Before using, the unit needs to be updated. 
1. Log in your account;
2. Ensure the DBScar connector is in 16 PIN DLC under the dash (see the picture below);
3. Connect the DBScar connector via Bluetooth;
4. Turn the ignition switch to ON position;
Caution: Disconnect the DBScar connector from DLC during the update will permanent damage the vehicle and device!
